transcripts: Style can certainly be worked out. That's why Axe recommends the spiked-up look. First, mix the glue in your hands. Then rake your hair energetically. Congrats, you just burned 2 calories. finally twist it hard. Awesome. But of course he's not just a pretty hairstyle. He can shoot a text right from his arm band. Exquisite emoji choice. Mix, rake, twist. Easy for every day.
